      About this item

      • A GENTLE GLOW LEADS THE WAY. When your little one is asleep, let a soft light beneath their crib or bed light the way. Our Under Crib Smart Light helps you check on your child without waking them upor stubbing your toe in the dark. This unique light is part of our Connected Suite which puts parents in control of their childs sleep atmosphere through our family-friendly, easy-to-use Safety 1st Connected App.
      • DONT WAKE LITTLE ONE. Raise or dim the Under Crib Smart Light without ever entering the roomtap the control settings within the app to make changes from wherever you are.
      • BABYS FIRST LIGHT SHOW. Customize lighting brightness and colors or choose from six recommended lighting pre-sets (Night Task, Night Red, Relax White, Story Time, Relaxing Colorful, Wake Up) all from within the Safety 1st Connected App. The in-app color wheel lets you match the lighting color to your nursery dcor.
      • BUILT-IN MOTION AND AMBIENT LIGHT SENSOR. The built-in sensor is motion activated and automatically dims after your custom set period of inactivity. Additionally, establish your preferred motion detection distance and ambient light settings within the app, so it illuminates the room exactly when and the way you want it to.

      Product Description

      Our Under Crib Smart Light gently glows beneath your little ones crib or bed, so you wont wake them during check-ins. Automatically activated with a built-in motion sensor. Customize lighting brightness and colors or select from six recommended lighting pre-sets. This unique light uses the Safety 1st Connected App which is the only app that empowers parents to create the optimal environment, set the mood, monitor, and comfort their childanytime, from anywhere. This easy-to-use, family friendly app seamlessly controls and manages every device in the Connected Suite giving parents the confidence and peace of mind they need to stay connected to their child even when theyre apart.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      4 out of 5 stars
      Nice connected smart LED in Safety 1st system
      So for what this is, a small LED light strip with a PIR motion sensor, it is a bit expensive. So what you're really paying for is the app connectivity for the smart controls.So, can you use this without the app? Sort of. When it starts up, it will be red in pairing mode. You have to wait for it to eventually turn white and then the button can toggle between motion/on/off. But without the app you cannot change the LED color or set other things like slow turn off. Also if it ever looses power, it will go back to pairing mode red LED and then just on. So no, I would not recommend using this without the app.So with the app, it is pretty nice. Pairing with the app is fairly easy, especially since it enters pairing mode when powered on (red LEDs). The app allows for a lot of controls, like changing the current state (on/off/motion), the color, configuring slow turn off, and more. It comes with a very long USB cord to reach a power source from where the crib is located.Once you have it set up with the app and everything it works well, but there is one issue to be aware of: when it looses power (say, a power outage or blip) it will turn back on until it syncs back to the WiFi and returns to the last setting. That is pretty irritating.
